Release:        1%{?dist}
Summary:        Java plugin based web server
License:        ASL 2.0
Group:          Development/Libraries/Java
URL:            https://geronimo.apache.org/xbean/
Source0:        http://repo2.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/%{name}/%{name}/%{version}/%{name}-%{version}-source-release.zip
